  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose is to evaluate neuropsychological effects of anterior temporal epilepsy in face
      perception by comparison of performances of epileptic patients and control individuals, sex-,
      age- and socio-educational level-matched.

      Secondary purposes are to prospectively evaluate neuropsychological impact of anterior
      temporal lobectomy performed for surgical treatment of anterior temporal epilepsy on face
      perception (exploratory study).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
